::Killfest/Incarcinator::

Killfest and Incarcinator walk up to Scyther and Killfest, seeing 
that the two had been waiting to be let in to the Blackfortress for 
some time. Killfest taps his comm.

"DrillBit, I have returned. Tell Darkfate to lower the bridge so that 
me and my team can enter."
